                        </h3>
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-baseline mb-4 mt-8">
                            <span class="mr-2 text-5xl font-extrabold text-ttblue">$1</span> <span
                                class="text-ttblue">/1,000 requests</span>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-sm mb-4">Minimum charge of $5/mo</span>
                        <ul role="list" class="mb-8 space-y-4 mt-4 text-left">
                            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                                <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-ttblue" fill="currentColor"
                                     viewbox="0 0 20 20"
                                     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                    <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                                          d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z"
                                          clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                                </svg>
                                <span>Unlimited requests</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                                <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-ttblue" fill="currentColor"
                                     viewbox="0 0 20 20"
                                     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
